we're not just gonna
let these criminals go, right?

2224
01:34:55,355 --> 01:34:56,988
Ah, come on, commish.
Let's face it.

2225
01:34:56,990 --> 01:34:59,156
Those guys are no match
for the four of us.

2226
01:34:59,158 --> 01:35:00,992
We'll give them
a 30-minute head start.

2227
01:35:00,994 --> 01:35:03,794
Besides, you can't fight crime
on an empty stomach.

2228
01:35:06,531 --> 01:35:07,932
Hey, computer?

2229
01:35:07,934 --> 01:35:09,266
We're home!

2230
01:35:12,804 --> 01:35:14,105
<i> What is the password?</i>

2231
01:35:14,107 --> 01:35:15,840
Iron man sucks!

2232
01:35:27,853 --> 01:35:29,053
When dad
and me were fighting,

2233
01:35:29,055 --> 01:35:30,788
I was giving them
my best one-liners.

2234
01:35:31,523 --> 01:35:32,590
<i> You</i>

2235
01:35:34,693 --> 01:35:36,394
<i> complete me.</i>

2236
01:35:49,641 --> 01:35:52,743
Holy family photo, Batman.
I love it!

2237
01:35:59,651 --> 01:36:01,052
<i> White.</i>

2238
01:36:01,054 --> 01:36:05,656
<i> All important movies end</i>
<i> with a white screen.</i>

2239
01:36:05,658 --> 01:36:07,892
<i> And tying up loose ends.</i>

2240
01:36:07,894 --> 01:36:10,161
We're coming for you,
Gotham city!

2241
01:36:10,163 --> 01:36:11,695
<i> Like </i>
<i> this snake clowns bit.</i>

2242
01:36:11,697 --> 01:36:12,930
<i> Snake clowns?</i>

2243
01:36:12,932 --> 01:36:14,598
<i> Told you </i>
<i> they were real.</i>

2244
01:36:14,600 --> 01:36:16,333
<i> Did you stick wigs </i>
<i> onto snakes?</i>

2245
01:36:16,335 --> 01:36:18,369
<i>- Maybe.</i>
<i>- That is so weird.</i>

2246
01:36:18,371 --> 01:36:19,937
<i> Can I play that song </i>
<i> I wrote for the end credits?</i>

2247
01:36:19,939 --> 01:36:21,205
<i> That is a hard pass.</i>

2248
01:36:21,207 --> 01:36:23,074
<i>- Come on.</i>
<i>- No!</i>

2249
01:36:23,076 --> 01:36:24,508
<i> Let the kid play </i>
<i> whatever music he wants.</i>

2250
01:36:24,510 --> 01:36:25,743
<i>- No, no, no!</i>
<i>- Please?</i>

2251
01:36:25,745 --> 01:36:26,911
<i>- No.</i>
- Padre?

2252
01:36:26,913 --> 01:36:28,679
<i> Fine. 'Puter.</i>

2253
01:36:28,681 --> 01:36:30,014
<i> Okay, sir.</i>

2254
01:36:30,016 --> 01:36:31,949
<i> Yay!</i>

2255
01:36:31,951 --> 01:36:33,918
<i> Now playing </i>
<i> Robin's happy, poppy music.</i>

2256
01:36:33,920 --> 01:36:37,254
<i> The kind that makes parents</i>
<i> and studio executives happy.</i>

2257
01:37:00,946 --> 01:37:02,012
Come on, everyone!

2258
01:37:21,566 --> 01:37:22,967
Come on, Batman!
No!

2259
01:38:50,188 --> 01:38:52,823
Wow, that was fun!

2260
01:38:52,825 --> 01:38:55,359
Really hope
nobody was recording that.

2261
01:38:55,361 --> 01:38:56,927
Let me see.
Oh, this thing is on.

2262
01:38:56,929 --> 01:38:57,928
This thing is recording.
